m slot in the game.&amp;nbsp; I am happy with my DoDH charm aug, but I wouldnt refuse the ability to raid for better augs either.&amp;nbsp; I personally think the Charm slot should be given over to the Tradeskillers, with each different skill making a different style of Charm, and the "best" Charms be aquired via people making attunable items and selling them&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
